# UI Language: English Only

All user-facing UI text in this project must be in **English**.

- Labels, buttons, placeholders, hints, error messages, toast content
- Any string shown to end users in the SilentPassUI app

Do not use Chinese or other languages for UI display. Use English for all visible text.
